@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_phfjav(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v0 = v0
    tmp = wp.sin(wp.cos((v2 + 0.09 - v0 + 0.65)))
    v2 = ((wp.sin(v2 + 0.69) - tmp) / 0.04)
    v1 = tmp
    v2 = (((v1 + 0.83 * tmp + 0.19) + (v2 + 0.96 * v2 + 0.64)) * 0.64)
    v1 = (wp.sin((tmp + 0.27 * v2 + 0.44)) + 0.24)
    v1 = v2
    v0 = wp.exp(wp.exp(wp.sin(v1 + 0.97)))
    data[tid] = v0
